-download MLO from https://github.com/BharatRaj-G/EmbeddedLinux/tree/master/BeagleBone_LinuxBuild/AngstromDistribution/Angstrom-v2012.12%20-%202013.06.20
-Partition the uSD Card into two 
	Partition 1 - FAT (BOOT) - around 1GB
	Partition 2 - Ext3 (ROOTFS)

-Set "boot" flag for BOOT partition
-Copy MLO to BOOT partition
-Eject SD Card and insert to BBB.


-Power the BBB with S2 pressed
-Following messages appear

U-Boot SPL 2013.04-dirty (Jun 19 2013 - 09:57:14)
